comments: Porzingis (DAL) intentionally kicks the ball.
Finney-Smith (DAL) and Durant (BKN) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
Doncic (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position as he defends Harden's (BKN) drive to the basket.
Johnson (BKN) places his hand momentarily on Doncic?s hip before immediately removing his hand.
Johnson (BKN) makes contact with Porzingis' (DAL) arm that affects his shot near the rim.
Durant (BKN) makes marginal contact with Finney-Smith (DAL) off ball that does not affect his ability to defend the pass in the post.
Finney-Smith (DAL) legally contest Durant's (BKN) shot attempt.
Porzingis (DAL) is already in Johnson's (BKN) path and is firming up when contact occurs.

The foul called on Harden (BKN) was reviewed on replay by virtue of coach?s challenge.  Replay review correctly overturned the foul call.  Harden makes contact with the ball and dislodges it from Doncic (DAL) during his drive. After the ball is dislodged and control lost, there is incidental contact to Doncic?s hand/wrist.
Mills (BKN) moves along Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) path defending his driving shot attempt and marginal contact occurs.
Porzingis (DAL) makes marginal contact with Durant (BKN) and disengages as they pursue the loose ball.
Porzingis (DAL) makes contact to Johnson's (BKN) body that affects his ability to gather the loose ball.
Finney-Smith (DAL) and Durant (BKN) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
Doncic (DAL) makes contact with Claxton's (BKN) arm that affects his shot near the rim.
Doncic (DAL)  briefly engages with Claxton (BKN) after the screen.
Powell (DAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Johnson's (BKN) path and absorbs the contact.
Porzingis (DAL) extends his arm and dislodges Durant (BKN) from his position during rebounding.
Doncic (DAL) hands off the ball in Brown's (BKN) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Harden (BKN) places his hands against Doncic's (DAL) chest after the release of his pass and the contact is marginal.
Durant (BKN) makes marginal contact with Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt.
